{"tid":2166601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[哩單都好鬼］前黑警‘二姐’ 現任申訴專員趙慧賢 主動調查私營機構打疫苗","createTime":"2020-08-20T13:47:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T01:15:43.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"de009c2ca59cebe5981161f314fb4a40c257d9ab","tid":2166601,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:47:14.000Z","msg":"懷疑想阻止私家醫生等打外國肺炎疫苗 迫用國貨<br />\n否則日後買國貨冇人打咪好柒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544843-20200820.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544843-20200820.htm&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5UzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=7da328a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544843-20200820.htm&h=2c6bb026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544843-20200820.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n申訴專員公署宣布，主動調查政府現行監管本港私營醫療機構提供疫苗的機制，有否可改善之處。公署指出，去年7月衞生署與海關發現，有醫務中心涉嫌提供冒牌九價子宮頸癌疫苗，樣本對接種者可能帶來風險。<br />\n<br />\n申訴專員趙慧賢說，本港出現懷疑水貨或冒牌九價子宮頸癌疫苗，主因是市場對該疫苗需求量大但供應有限，以致有不法分子將平行進口或冒牌的疫苗，提供給私營醫療機構。當局其後按既定機制跟進，並加強監管措施，公署將會探究現行監管機制的成效，以及有否可改善之處，並會向食物及衞生局、衞生署及海關進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n申訴專員趙慧賢說，市面出現不合規格，甚至假冒的疫苗製品，會危害市民健康，因此必須做好把關的工作，進一步改善現行監管機制的方法。"},{"pid":"bb8a74a5fa445ec12ba41c173e60a356d08dc3ce","tid":2166601,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:48:09.000Z","msg":"可能想落格姐，國家要充公外國疫苗"},{"pid":"90c20b0e4c93f3b740cf8dfac33723737fc2610a","tid":2166601,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"今年4月出任申訴專員的趙慧賢，是警務處前副處長，她上任時說過，為釋除外界疑慮，所有與警務處有關的投訴個案，她都不會參與。公署昨回覆查詢時表示，趙慧賢「已委派副申訴專員全權處理對警務處的投訴，她本人沒有處理。」副申訴專員蘇錦成是前AO、民政事務局前副秘書長。曾蔭權早年做政務司司長時，蘇錦成是曾蔭權的政務助理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/24068/申訴專員公署-趙慧賢-香港警務處-24068/申訴專員6至9月接逾千宗涉警隊投訴-前「二姐」交副手處理\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F24068%2F%E7%94%B3%E8%A8%B4%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2-%E8%B6%99%E6%85%A7%E8%B3%A2-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E8%99%95-24068%2F%E7%94%B3%E8%A8%B4%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A16%E8%87%B39%E6%9C%88%E6%8E%A5%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E5%AE%97%E6%B6%89%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4-%E5%89%8D%E3%80%8C%E4%BA%8C%E5%A7%90%E3%80%8D%E4%BA%A4%E5%89%AF%E6%89%8B%E8%99%95%E7%90%86&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5UzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=30b53ad6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/24068/申訴專員公署-趙慧賢-香港警務處-24068/申訴專員6至9月接逾千宗涉警隊投訴-前「二姐」交副手處理</a>"},{"pid":"e0826e667a96a0c6365b4ab982dcfe33c5866e12","tid":2166601,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f9a67ef597fbac85c47b3c49c2428dacc5d4d3","tid":2166601,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bb8a74a5fa445ec12ba41c173e60a356d08dc3ce","tid":2166601,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:48:09.000Z","msg":"可能想落格姐，國家要充公外國疫苗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:31:28.000Z","msg":"問題點解係申訴專員調查<br />\n而唔係HA?<br />\n<br />\n私營機構關佢乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1bbe74aa73c0aae8e142e6c809571eb66dc32a","tid":2166601,"uid":4964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f7f9a67ef597fbac85c47b3c49c2428dacc5d4d3","tid":2166601,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bb8a74a5fa445ec12ba41c173e60a356d08dc3ce","tid":2166601,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:48:09.000Z","msg":"可能想落格姐，國家要充公外國疫苗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T15:31:28.000Z","msg":"問題點解係申訴專員調查<